:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Victor\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1112:\"<p>We&#8217;re pleased to announce that <strong>Event Tickets Plus 4.10.1.3</strong> is now available.</p>\n<p>In most cases you will be able to take advantage of automated updates, but if those are unavailable for any reason you can download the plugins from your <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/my-account/downloads/\">downloads page</a> then <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/manual-updates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">update manually</a>.</p>\n<h3>Event Tickets Plus 4.10.1.3</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Correct issue with WooCommerce ticket charges not being sent to Stripe and other gateways</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks for your patience and support while we worked on this issue <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/announcing-event-tickets-plus-4-10-1-3/\">Announcing Event Tickets Plus 4.10.1.3</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"Announcing Event Tickets 4.10.1.2 and Event Tickets Plus 4.10.1.2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\