76-Attendee-Registration-Page-Template\">Attendee Registration Page Template</a>. We&#8217;ve also included a way for event creators to check in attendees via the front end attendee list within Community Tickets.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-schedule/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Maintenance Releases</a> are smaller updates between major updates that are mostly comprised of bug fixes, tweaks, and small but meaningful improvements.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#et\">Event Tickets 4.10.1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#etp\">Event Tickets Plus 4.10.1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#ce\">Community Events 4.6.1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#ct\">Community Tickets 4.6.1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#not-updated\">Not Updated This Release</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"et\">Event Tickets 4.10.1</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Feature</strong> &#8211; Add Promoter access from the WP Admin Bar</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Update the order of loading of providers to ensure correct execution for Promoter</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Only show attendee registration for RSVP if going</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Fix broken ticket block sagas to allow syncing with event times</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Only allow attendee move functionality in admin</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Add filter to allow plugins to bypass the checkin caps requirement (for community events)</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Filter <samp>the_excerpt</samp> to prevent loading it on the CE attendee registration page</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Allow users to always access attendee registration page if tickets in cart have meta</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Allow tickets with required and non-required meta to be saved together</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Fix issue with WooCommerce checkout returning to attendee registration page</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Update available tickets when updating capacity</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Do not show print, email, and export buttons if not in admin</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Add Indian Rupee and Russian Ruple to PayPal currency code list</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Fix RSVP &#8220;don&#8217;t show my information&#8221; checkbox in Twenty Nineteen theme</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Add ticket id to option id for attendee registration fields</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Path to override attendee registration templates defined in template files</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Fix path to override attendee registration templates</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Fix text domain in attendee field view</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Fix focus for sales duration in ticket block</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Fix mobile styles for tickets and RSVP</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Prevent notices when adding a new event in Community Events with Community Tickets</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Modify how the status manager initializes to use class names instead of proper names, which might be translated</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Prevent fatal errors on front end ticket page if the provider is deactivated</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Add a new setting to set a threshold on whether to show the &#8220;Display # tickets left&#8221; along with a new filter <samp>tribe_tickets_left_threshold</samp></li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Add duration error for duration issues with ticket and RSVP</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Save attendee information on registration page via ajax</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Make clipboard icon for ticket block a tooltip and persistent</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Indicate required fields in ticket block</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Add filter for attendee registration page template</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Add filter to manage attendees permissions</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Add filter to allow email form to be shown for non-admins</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Added filters:\n<ul>\n<li><samp>tribe_tickets_attendee_registration_page_template</samp></li>\n<li><samp>tribe_tickets_user_can_manage_attendees</samp></li>\n<li><samp>tribe_allow_admin_on_frontend</samp></li>\n<li><samp>tribe_display_tickets_left_threshold</samp></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Changed views:\n<ul>\n<li><samp>registration/attendees/content</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/attendees/error</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/attendees/fields</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/attendees/fields/checkbox</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/attendees/fields/radio</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/attendees/fields/select</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/attendees/fields/text</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/attendees/loader</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/attendees/success</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/button-cart</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/button-checkout</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/cart-empty</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/content</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/content</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/description</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/registration-status</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/ticket/content</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/icon-svg</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/ticket/icon</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/ticket/price</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/ticket/quantity</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/ticket/title</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/tickets-header</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/tickets</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/title</samp></li>\n<li><samp>registration/summary/toggle-handler</samp></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Language</strong> &#8211; 7 new strings added, 140 updated, 1 fuzzied, and 2 obsoleted</li>\n<li><strong>LanguageÂ (Tribe Common)Â </strong> &#8211; 0 new strings added, 0 updated, 1 fuzzied, and 0 obsoleted</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"etp\">Event Tickets Plus 4.10.1</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Fix bug on classic RSVP for mobile viewport</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Only show attendee registration for RSVP if going</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Allow users to always access attendee registration page if tickets in cart have meta</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Allow tickets with required and non-required meta to be saved together</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Fix mobile styles for tickets and RSVP</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Prevent fatal errors on front end ticket page if the provider is deactivated</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Allow empty checkboxes as valid if they are the only field</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Don&#8217;t add extra checkboxes for empty lines</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Added setting in Settings-&gt;Tickets-&gt;WooCommerce to turn off attendee generation delay</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Add wp ajax action to save attendee meta</li>\n<li><strong>Tweak</strong> &#8211; Added filter: <samp>tribe_tickets_woo_settings</samp></li>\n<li><strong>Language</strong> &#8211; 9 new strings added, 23 updated, 1 fuzzied, and 0 obsoleted</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"ce\">Community Events 4.6.1</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Allow event creators to check in attendees via the front end attendee list (applicable only when Community Tickets is also installed)</li>\n<li><strong>Language</strong> &#8211; 0 new strings added, 64 updated, 0 fuzzied, and 0 obsoleted</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"ct\">Community Tickets 4.6.1</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; Allow event creators to check in attendees via the front end attendee list</li>\n<li><strong>Fix</strong> &#8211; 